posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'You will absolutely be AMAZED with our community here at Woodland Park.', 'Enjoy your balcony or patio that overlooks a natural park-like setting or take a stroll along the river in the evenings.', '12-15 Month Lease Options Now Available for a Limited-Time Only!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Private Garage Space Available', 'For Rent', '- Community Picnic Areas', '- Large Bedrooms With Tons Of Closet Space', '- Intercom Controlled Entry Access Systems', '- Standard Dominium Comfort Package', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & Cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Woodland Park participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Make the move today by giving our professional staff a call:', 'show contact info', 'Woodland Park', '2614 Cutters Grove Ave Clubhouse', 'Anoka, MN, 55303', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'hxOmwMG2']
